boxes.label: Aerial view from Google Earth displaying a pair of small airplanes on a tarmac area with no visible resolution information. The airplanes are white with dark accents, oriented in a similar direction, and they are approximately equal in size, with one positioned closer to the top edge of the image and another closer to the bottom edge.
